content:
Janamaddhye ninnu kanaanya-sthree kenuchatthil
Mashihaa! Krpa thonnanamennil-krpayaal prerithanaayu
/tnijasrshdikalle-rogakleshangall
/tneekki kaappaan-nee lokam pooki
Ghoraduraathmaavil ninnum-rakshikken makalle.
Srshdiye sandarshichone! Naathhaa sthuthiyevam
/thaaleluyyaa-raapakalavall paadum.
